<section id="content">

<blockquote>
	<q>The twelve notes in each octave and the varieties of rhythm offer me opportunities that all of human genius will never exhaust.</q>
	<cite><a href="/author/143">Igor Stravinsky</a></cite>
	<footer>contributed by <a href="/contributor/483">monique</a></footer>
</blockquote>

